INSERT INTO `teams` VALUES (1,'Payas Agarwal','Director','teams/1745923038_payas1_png','teams/1745923038_payas1_png','Great Value Payas Agarwal Noida','An MBA graduate from Babson College, he brings over five years of hands-on experience in leading and managing the Group. A visionary strategist and analytical leader, he is deeply committed to staying informed about the latest industry developments and market trends. His forward-thinking approach and ability to adapt to dynamic environments have been instrumental in driving growth and fostering innovation within the organization.',1,1,1,'2025-02-19 04:26:51','2025-04-29 10:37:18'),(3,'Amit Goel','Fund Manager','teams/1741676702.2.png','teams/1742300939.amit-goel.png','Great Value Amit Goel Noida','Key figure in distressed asset turnarounds, bringing 25+ years of experience across global firms like Millennium Global, Viridian Partners, Swamih Fund and TruBoard Partners. Has raised and managed $350Mn+ in AUM.',0,7,1,'2025-02-19 05:12:00','2025-05-28 07:55:20'),(4,'Manoj Agarwal','Chairman & MD, GV Group','teams/1745923178_manoj1_png','teams/1745923178_manoj1_png','Great Value Manoj Agarwal Noida','Mr. Manoj Agarwal stands as the cornerstone of the Great Value Group, steering its transformation from a modest glassware enterprise to a diverse and thriving conglomerate over the past three decades. With a keen business instinct and an unwavering vision, he has led the Group to remarkable success across multiple industries. After completing his education in Bangalore, Mr. Agarwal joined the family business, which became the foundation for his entrepreneurial journey. He seized an opportunity to venture into food processing for the Uttar Pradesh Government, establishing a stable and successful foothold in the food industry. Building on this success, he expanded into real estate, acquiring assets that have led to the development of prominent projects, enriching the lives of countless buyers. Driven by his motto of adding value to people’s lives, Mr. Agarwal ensures that his efforts have a positive impact, both directly and indirectly. Committed to social responsibility, he dedicates 10% of his personal income to extensive CSR initiatives and welfare activities across India. He is actively involved with organizations such as Divya Prem Seva Mission and Bhaurav Devras Seva Nyas. Additionally, he has independently established five dispensaries and a primary school in Delhi NCR, underscoring his commitment to community development.Mr. Manoj Agarwal’s journey is a testament to visionary leadership, innovation, and a deep sense of responsibility toward society.',1,1,1,'2025-02-19 05:12:50','2025-04-29 10:39:38'),(5,'Goldie Kapoor','Sales and Marketing Head','teams/1745923268_GoldieKapoor1_png','teams/1745923268_GoldieKapoor1_png','Great Value Goldie Kapoor Noida','Goldie is a seasoned and dedicated professional in the group with over 23 years of expertise in residential sales, retail, warehousing, and industrial leasing alongside significant experience in evaluating and analyzing stressed asset investments. A result-driven individual with a proven history of identifying opportunities and delivering strategies that optimize financial growth and operational efficiency.',0,9,1,'2025-02-19 05:13:26','2025-04-29 10:41:08'),(7,'Nakul Goel','CFO','teams/1745923346_NakulGoel1_png','teams/1745923346_NakulGoel1_png','Great Value Nakul Goel Noida','Experienced financial professional with over 25 years of expertise in financial management, corporate financial law, investment operations, banking practices, and risk management. Possesses extensive knowledge in assessing the financial health of investments through advanced data analysis and forecasting, driving strategic financial decision-making and sustainable growth.',0,6,1,'2025-02-21 18:53:30','2025-04-29 10:42:26'),(10,'Nidhi Jain','Head of Procurement','teams/1741676493.6.png','teams/1742358148.nidhi-jain.png','Great Value Nidhi Jain Noida','A graduate of the prestigious Shri Ram College of Commerce, Nidhi Jain pursued her academic journey in Economics Honours, laying a strong foundation in the principles of economics and business.',0,3,1,'2025-03-10 12:46:28','2025-07-01 11:09:21'),(12,'R.S Sharma','Head of Liaisoning','teams/1741676867.7.png','teams/1742358197.rs-sharma.png','Great Value R.S Sharma Noida','RS Sharma is an experienced professional in the field of liaisoning, responsible for fostering and managing relationships between the organization and external stakeholders. As the Head of Liaisoning, he plays a crucial role in ensuring smooth communication and coordination with government bodies, regulatory authorities, and other key partners.',0,5,1,'2025-03-10 12:48:42','2025-07-01 11:13:31'),(13,'Aditya Garg','Accounts Head','teams/1741677003.8.png','teams/1742358236.aditya.png','Great Value Aditya Garg Noida','Aditya Garg is an accomplished professional with extensive experience in managing and overseeing accounting operations. As the Accounts Head, he plays a pivotal role in ensuring accurate financial reporting, budget management, and strategic financial planning. With a keen eye for detail and a deep understanding of financial principles',0,4,1,'2025-03-10 12:49:49','2025-07-01 11:13:09'),(14,'Aakash Kataria','Investment Analyst','teams/1741677057.9.png','teams/1742358265.akash.png','Great Value Akash Kataria Noida','With high-profile accolades in financial analysis like the Harvard GCC and AIBC, and 2+ years of experience working in Founder’s Office and research in Economics, Aakash brings expertise in critically analyzing and evaluating opportunities.',0,8,1,'2025-03-10 12:50:25','2025-07-01 09:00:46'),(15,'Adhvika Agarwal','Director of Sales and Marketing','teams/1741677196.10.png','teams/1742358292.adhvika.png','Great Value Adhvika Agarwal Noida','Adhvika Agarwal holds a Master’s in Entrepreneurship from Cass Business School and a BSc (Hons) in Management Studies from the University of Nottingham. With a strong academic foundation and a passion for business, she brings a strategic mindset to her professional endeavours.',0,2,1,'2025-03-10 12:51:09','2025-07-01 08:52:44'),(16,'Ranjeet Bhalla','Head of CRM','teams/1745928796_RanjeetBhalla_png','teams/1745928796_RanjeetBhalla_png','Great Value Ranjeet Bhalla Noida','Ranjeet Bhalla is a seasoned professional with extensive expertise in customer relationship management (CRM). As the Head of CRM, he is responsible for developing and implementing strategies that enhance customer engagement, satisfaction, and retention.',0,10,1,'2025-03-10 13:15:49','2025-07-01 11:13:46');
